2026-05-20T22:35:38.9332233Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-20T22:35:38.9333108Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-20T22:35:38.9333858Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-20T22:35:38.9334651Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-20T22:35:38.9335622Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-20T22:35:38.9336499Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-20T22:35:38.9357753Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
