2026-05-20T22:35:39.6205004Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-20T22:35:39.6205359Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-20T22:35:39.6205707Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-20T22:35:39.6206011Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
